                <note rend="inline" type="source">123J634/343: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-06-06T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 6, 1935—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>151. Your 115, May 22, 4 p.m. The President desires to appoint you as Ambassador
                    to China. Request <hi rend="italic">agrément</hi> of Chinese Government and
                    telegraph reply as early as possible.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
